---
import { ArrowRight } from 'lucide-astro';
---

<section class="relative min-h-[90vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden pt-20">
  <!-- Background effects -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 -left-20 w-64 h-64 md:w-96 md:h-96 bg-electric-blue/10 blur-[80px] md:blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 -right-20 w-64 h-64 md:w-96 md:h-96 bg-neon-violet/10 blur-[80px] md:blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center" data-aos="fade-up">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 mb-6 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase border border-white/20 rounded-full bg-charcoal-grey/30 backdrop-blur-md">
        Marketing + Desarrollo Web
      </span>
      
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-bold mb-8 leading-tight">
        Más que contenido, <br class="hidden sm:block" />
        <span class="text-gradient">Estrategia Digital</span> <br class="hidden sm:block" />
        de Alto Rendimiento
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-white/70 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Gasty Creative escala tu marca con una fusión técnica única: dominamos los algoritmos de redes sociales tanto como el código detrás de una landing de alta conversión.
      </p>
      
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://wa.me/5491164246726" target="_blank" class="group relative px-8 py-4 bg-electric-blue text-black font-bold rounded-xl overflow-hidden transition-all hover:glow-blue hover:scale-105 active:scale-95">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            Impulsa tu Marca
            <ArrowRight class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" />
          </span>
        </a>
        <a href="#portfolio" class="px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-all hover:bg-white/10">
          Mis Trabajos
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce opacity-40">
    <div class="w-1 h-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-b from-electric-blue to-transparent"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 8vw, 6rem);
  }
</style>
